  <h1 class="page-title"><span property="schema:name" class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">To know how it works, see how it moves</span>
</h1>

                
                      <a href="/content/list-by-author/Marianne+Freiberger">Marianne Freiberger</a>                <a class="plus-share-button" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Share this page!"
           data-title="To know how it works, see how it moves" data-url="https://plus.maths.org/know-how-it-works-see-how-it-moves" data-description="Article from Plus">Share this page</a>
      </div>
